--- !u!114 &465100413
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 465100411}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 43aaff53c6a392941b7c17d0dfd87d94, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1413781446}
  dialogue:
  - dialogueName: Priest
    dialogueText: Why ! do you! Persist! You snake in the garden. wretched mewling
      thing that befouls these poor souls
  - dialogueName: Priest
    dialogueText: 'Your wrath against all that is good will never be satiated, you
      will never feel the warmth and comfort of love. You will never feel the absolution
      that you deny these poor things '
  - dialogueName: Priest
    dialogueText: 'Your parents should feel shame at what hollow antithesis of a
      man they have created. How they have failed to teach you the simplest of virtues.
      how they have let your malice blight this world  '
  - dialogueName: Priest
    dialogueText: 'I would tell you to leave, but that is pointless. you seem set
      on your track. just know its destination lies with me and I will afford you
      the same mercy you have shown to my flock '
  - dialogueName: Hunter
    dialogueText: 'Mercy? Fucking mercy!!!! What do you think I''ve been doing? what
      I''m doing is a mercy. And my mother was a great woman who taught me kindness
      and laughter, and who taught me to love and care. '
  - dialogueName: Hunter
    dialogueText: 'She would know I''m putting these poor things out of their misery
      and she would would be proud of me. If there was any other option I would go
      for it straight away! believe me  '
  - dialogueName: Watch
    dialogueText: 'Boss don''t listen to him, You are strong and kind, you''re doing
      a difficult thing for a good reason, he is just angry and lashing out '
  - dialogueName: Hunter
    dialogueText: "He is angry I'm hurting the ghosts. but he\u2019s the one leading
      them here. It's his fault they\u2019re being corrupted and he needs to know
      this. He needs to answer to so much. "
  - dialogueName: Watch
    dialogueText: 'Then keep going and don''t let him get to you. I know you can
      do this Hunter. '
  audio1: {fileID: 1048820864}
  audio2: {fileID: 0}
